Escúchame.

00:27:03.620 --> 00:27:04.440
Shen.

00:27:06.010 --> 00:27:06.460
Señora.

00:27:06.460 --> 00:27:07.660
¿De dónde

00:27:07.660 --> 00:27:08.570
